# ── Ollama (local, always free) ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Requires Ollama running locally: https://ollama.ai
# ollama pull phi4:latest && ollama pull gemma3:4b
LLM_PROVIDER=ollama
LLM_API_KEY=ollama
LLM_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434
LLM_MODEL=gemma3:4b

# ── Groq (free cloud tier, recommended) ───────────────────────────────────────
# Sign up at https://console.groq.com — no credit card required.
# Free tier: ~30 req/min, 14,400 req/day for llama-3.3-70b-versatile.
# When set, all agents automatically prefer Groq over local Ollama.
# Remove or leave blank to use Ollama only.
# GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...

# ── Web Search (optional, for Researcher agent live search) ───────────────────
# Brave Search: https://api.search.brave.com
# BRAVE_SEARCH_API_KEY=

# Tavily (fallback search): https://tavily.com
# TAVILY_API_KEY=
